{
  "stem": "15576.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Judenrat, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] were the leaders, as I said before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they were-- they would come to them and say, he want this many, this many people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Another one, they start with the aktion, but you have to deliver.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then this stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they made Judenrein.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was very simple.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Anybody that saw a Jew has to kill them or report them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "If you do, you get everything the Jew has on them plus a reward.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And believe me, they didn't need incentives.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was brought-- brought up the fact, give you example about a person that comes as a guest and stays for weeks and overstays his visit.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Now, my family was with a Ukrainian family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Yeah, you credit where credit is do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Their life was in danger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They took you in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they keep you a month, two months, three months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the front is behind Moscow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And if somebody comes in, you're finished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the other ones, it-- it created, too, the other-- the other thing that happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Imagine there's three kinds of people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Good people that don't care, they don't mix in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Other keep-- people that keep you for a week or two, and they say, look, the front is behind Moscow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the biggest part were the ones that had benefits out of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took away everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they wanted them to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They don't need them anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And now this is Judenrat-- Judenrein.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Like I said, not-- anybody that sees somebody that--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, we knew already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we-- we knew that people were disappearing and nobody sees them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody ran away from one transport and told about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, we-- we knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Once you-- once you fall into their hands, that's it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
